no-ex-assign.description:
Description

This rule disallows reassigning exceptions incatchclauses.

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-ex-assign: "error"*/

try {
    // code
} catch (e) {
    e = 10;
}

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-ex-assign: "error"*/

try {
    // code
} catch (e) {
    const foo = 10;
}
